      "trigger": "Operator needs to enrich a Brand record with status and description after it has been auto-created",
      "prompt": "Create a new company called '[TEST] Oakwood Deli Chain'. They are a food-service business based in Bristol, United Kingdom. Their domain is testoakwooddeli.com.\n\nThen create a buyer deal called '[TEST] Oakwood Deli Chain - New Deal' in the Buyer Deal Pipeline at the Discovery stage. Associate the deal to the company. Associate the deal with the GLUG! client service so that a Brand record is auto-created.\n\nWait a few seconds for the Brand to be created by the workflow, then find the Brand record that was auto-created for this deal.\n\nOnce you have the Brand record, update it with the following:\n- Set hs_description to: 'Initial outreach to Oakwood — they run 12 deli sites across the South West. Key contact is Sarah Miles, Head of Procurement. Interested in chilled drinks for their grab-and-go counters.'\n- Set hs_status to: On Track\n\nConfirm the Brand was updated successfully by reading it back.",
